OL,4,Cgiven 14 year jail sentence in Russia
OL,6,FA bomb disposal expert from the Isle
OL,7,Fof Man who has been volunteering in
OL,8,FUkraine, has been sentenced to 14 \
OL,9,Fyears in jail by a Russian proxy court.
OL,11,FChristopher Garrett from Peel has
OL,12,Fdedicated years to clearing landmines
OL,13,Fin the war torn country but has now
OL,14,Fbeen convicted of terrorism charges in
OL,15,Fhis absence by a court under Russian
OL,16,Fcontrol.
