OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1744232007
OL,3,CBomb disposal expert from Isle of Man
OL,4,Cgiven 14 year jail sentence in Russia
OL,6,FIt is dangerous but necessary work
OL,7,Fwhich is why after previously working
OL,8,Fwith the Ukrainian National Guard -
OL,9,FChristopher has more recently co-
OL,10,Ffounded Prevail, a charity which
OL,11,Fprovides mine clearance training to
OL,12,Fothers. He says it's a mammoth task.
OL,14,F"It is going to take a very long time,
OL,15,Fthere's been some wild claims that
OL,16,Fwe're going to get the bulk of it done
OL,17,Fin the first 10 to 15 years and yes,
OL,18,Fpotentially large areas will get
OL,19,Fcleared in those times, but it's the
OL,20,Frest of it and it's going to take time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
