OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1744232007
OL,3,CBomb disposal expert from Isle of Man
OL,4,Cgiven 14 year jail sentence in Russia
OL,6,F"You know, we're still clearing
OL,7,FCambodia, we're still clearing places
OL,8,Flike Laos, Vietnam and that happened a
OL,9,Fvery long time ago so I think it's
OL,10,Fgoing to be at least 100 years."
OL,12,FChris says his work is helping to save
OL,13,Flives but a court in Donetsk which is
OL,14,Funder Russian control disagrees.
OL,16,FThey have sentenced him to 14 and a
OL,17,Fhalf years in jail on terrorism
OL,18,Fcharges in his absence which has left
OL,19,Fthe Isle of Man native bewildered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
