OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1744232007
OL,3,CBomb disposal expert from Isle of Man
OL,4,Cgiven 14 year jail sentence in Russia
OL,6,F"I don't really know what to say about
OL,7,Fit, the charges are ridiculous. I
OL,8,Fmean, charged for terrorism by
OL,9,Fvolunteering, or at times, being under
OL,10,Fcontract by the Ukrainian armed forces.
OL,12,F"I've not once stepped foot out of
OL,13,FUkraine towards, Belarus. I've never
OL,14,Fbeen to Russia, I've never been
OL,15,Finvolved in any actions directly on
OL,16,Fthe border."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
